        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And his oath unto Isaac: he made known to Isaac the oath which he swore to Abraham, and promised to perform it, Genesis 26:3, or concerning Isaac (a); in whom his seed was to be called, and in whose line from him the Messiah was to come, the grand article of this covenant. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "And his oath unto Isaac: he made known to Isaac the oath which he swore to Abraham, and promised to perform it, ",
            "children": []
